-- Merkel Rejects Joint EU Deposit Insurance for Foreseeable Future
-- B y   P a t r i c k   D o n a h u e
-- 2013-04-25T08:55:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-25/merkel-rejects-joint-eu-deposit-insurance-for-foreseeable-future.html
Germany  backs joint European bank
supervision “completely,” chancellor says.
*Germany rejects central deposit insurance “for the foreseeable
future,” backs coordinating insurance among euro countries:
Merkel
*Need mechanisms to ensure “deposit insurance is harmonized and
that a resolution mechanism is at least operating in euro
countries,” Merkel says
*Basel III rules must be implemented beyond Europe: Merkel
*Merkel comments in speech to savings bank officials in Dresden  To contact the reporter on this story:
